==English==

===Noun phrase===
'''golden ratio'''

#The [[irrational number]] (approximately 1·618033989), denoted by the [[Greek]] letter φ (phi), when the [[ratio]] of the “whole” ([[id est]], the sum of the larger and smaller parts) to the larger part is the same as the ratio of the larger part to the smaller part.

